values:
"For beautiful eyes, look for the good in others; for beautiful lips, speak only words of kindness; and for poise, walk with the knowledge that you are never alone." - Audrey Hepburn

THIS JOURNAL IS FRIENDS ONLY.
I like to meet interesting people with something to say. Even if you have different interests than me, I am willing to give it a try. Introduce yourself. Tell me your thoughts. It's nice to meet you. ♥

I know this is super annoying, but I have a new LJ due to the fact that soon, I will no longer be a MISS darcie. Also, I feel like this journal represents the old me I'm not proud of. I've grown up, and it's a new year, and I feel like a new person. So if you would like to be added, leave a comment at . I don't want to bother you at yours.
